{"type": "article", "id": 12991, "title": "需要“勤快”的灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-04T12:17:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154216UYCzAqBTlioGNmKf.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰设计工作室 Odd Matter Studio 最近推出了一系列特别有趣的灯具。不同于我们常见的灯具静止的开关设计，这些灯具想要开或者关，你都必须动一动手，就像是亲自完成一个电路的闭合和断开一样。这些灯具的外观设计干净利落，又充满复古的气息，即使摆着不动，看起来也是一件可爱的装饰品。这是<a href=\"http://oddmatterstudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\">工作室的主页</a>，点击可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140639CDhYM1EjGJF8OUKk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140641Oeirodh3MNyBjEU1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140641vj0hqEJBuZLIp3Ng.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140641az7ERAy4CldqhUoX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140642xQcofIGza3Zn6Ck0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140642hbcVOICJYaUv1rZN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.495\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140643nmbfz3txy9GrJvas.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261406430hbQUsn9kIT5K6G7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}